				The Rabbit.org Foundation
			
						
	


	
		

	
	
	
				We Know Bunnies.
			
						
	


	
		
	The authors and bunny educators you have trusted for over 30 years have come together to create a new rabbit.org website. We're honored to be the stewards of this trusted rabbit resource.

	


	
		
	Please join us in our quest to end the suffering, abuse, and exploitation of all rabbits through education and advocacy.

				Communities We Serve
			
						
	


	
		
	

	


	
		

	
	
	
				
				The Rabbit-Curious
				
			
					
			Are you a fan of all things lagomorph, or maybe you've been wondering if a bunny is right for you? We're here to help!	
			
	


	
		
	

	


	
		

	
	
	
				
				Rabbit Caretaker
				
			
					
			Are you a first-time rabbit caregiver, or perhaps you're a long-time bunny household needing some updated advice? We have resources to help everyone from novice to expert.	
			
	


	
		
	

	


	
		

	
	
	
				
				Shelters & Rescuers
				
			
					
			Are you a local rabbit rescuer, or perhaps you volunteer in a local shelter? We have resources to support and educate you and help you find community.	
			
	


	
		
	

	


	
		

	
	
	
				
				Veterinarians & Vet Techs
				
			
					
			Are you a part of the world of veterinary medicine? We have resources to support and educate you and help you find community.	
			
	



			
	
	
		
	How can we support you in your search for bunny knowledge and entertainment?
